### Admin Dashboard Controller Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@authToken = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Dashboard Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/metrics
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 2. Get Recent Actions (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/recent-actions/default
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 3. Get Recent Actions with Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/recent-actions?limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4. Get Recent Actions with Higher Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/recent-actions?limit=25
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 5. Get Recent Actions with Lower Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/recent-actions?limit=5
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 6. Get Recent Actions Maximum Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard/recent-actions?limit=50
Authorization: {{authToken}}
